assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n錯post? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw 英國今次都幾麻煩 brexit 都未搞掂又整個independence referendum"},{"pid":"d9edf8d8c9ebfcd4f5988b94414cf0a63f4fa540","tid":151401,"uid":36650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:42:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oIKmwpDDCIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoIKmwpDDCIo&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=95ac2f9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oIKmwpDDCIo</a><br />\n<br />\n【天氣報告】預料一道冷鋒會在今早橫過華南沿岸，與其相關的 東北季候風會在本週中後期為該區帶來清涼及多雲 的天氣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f9f253b5b1c555111a011de7662a9154895937","tid":151401,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:31:45.000Z","msg":"又話轉涼既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2593029fac6489176fb23dbc996213488014974","tid":151401,"uid":42440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:51:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又話轉涼既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係夜晚咩"},{"pid":"3a0089214e78b2cf42c17f15a9eeca5d2f85acb8","tid":151401,"uid":52405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:20:47.000Z","msg":"冷鋒宜加先過境 溫度正在下跌<br />\n收夜嘅手足記得着多件衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c0df08598cb1daecbf34315e0642657642d006","tid":151401,"uid":79363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T03:21:11.000Z","msg":"橫瀾島今朝先轉吹東北強風，港內應該仲要啲時間。<br />\n<br />\n帶左大遮出街，唔知落雨落到幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3658a65ff05d70b646a23cd5a907cc70f95ab0f","tid":151401,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T03:44:42.000Z","msg":"黑球 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21f4de4d976a9d69f0951837965ed5cbbe0f260","tid":151401,"uid":36650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T10:05:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8XBXs_TeTAs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8XBXs_TeTAs&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=e3177b91\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8XBXs_TeTAs</a><br />\n<br />\n【低溫預警】本台於2017年3月14日1800時向元朗、北區及大埔發出低溫預警。 <br />\n【天氣概況】 一道冷鋒已經喺今朝早橫過香港，而受隨後嘅東北季候風影響，本港正午時分大部分地區的氣溫較尋日低5至6度。預料東北季候風會喺未來幾日為華南沿岸地區帶來清涼同多雲嘅天氣。<br />\n⚠注意事項<br />\n⭕在冬春季交替時，天氣乍暖還寒。留意天氣轉變，適時增減衣物。<br />\n⭕打算參加水上運動或進行海上工作人士請特別小心，以防大風大浪帶來的危險。<br />\n⭕受不穩定天氣影響，留意天氣變化，適時帶備雨具。<br />\n⭕回南天非常潮濕，注意室內防潮。能見度低，注意交通安全。<br />\n================================================<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9c40d7f08f82b7da129c81c3b7f59eb65aa03c","tid":151401,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T10:30:32.000Z","msg":"呢度既風post點處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由我同櫻花負責開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家意見如何？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8d2f597a545ca3d0c4f1b255ace9563fad83b0","tid":151401,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T10:46:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢度既風post點處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由我同櫻花負責開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家意見如何？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n赤巴同馬sir都有呢到ac既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2453866b6afd984959819abc7ba02e20be3385","tid":151401,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T10:48:11.000Z","msg":"出面時事台班廢物15，16度已經講濕凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />趁呢個機會講下點解香港體感通常低過外國啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1，香港無暖氣，外國有，令人感覺室外都好似無咁凍<br />\n<br />\n2，香港較低緯，冷空氣一定要南下先影響到，所以香港台灣凍既時候九成大風，大北風定大東風都有返咁上下風，同時即使係較乾既北風，好多時都令香港多雲陰天無太陽；<br />\n外國比較高緯，佢地凍既方式多數係成個冷高壓壓頂，所以溫度低過香港同時接近無風，而佢地好多時係夜晚凍朝早好好太陽，咁樣自然係香港感覺凍d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事實上凍無一個指標係關濕度事，只有風寒指數，係關風事，但若果落雨就另一回事，好似猛太陽體感高幾度咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw外國只係多數凍得黎無風，但若果有風基本一定凍過香港，日本富山金澤新潟果邊係食晒冬天風個風向，大風到頭都甩之餘體感都凍到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外日本因為島國關係，風大既冬季日子唔少，所以對歐亞大陸多數凍得較細風既外國人黎講，佢地都覺日本既5度凍過自己地方既5度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講，係同樣無雨無太陽情況下（有太陽一定熱d唔使講），關鍵係風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然溫度都重要，15-20再大風都係涼，10-15有風已經feel到刺刺地骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後打直落既雨凍過打直落既雪，但暴風雪凍過暴風雨，因為大風d雪打落你到，融雪最凍，你用你身體融雪吸走勁多熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以所謂香港濕凍係陰天加大風，外國乾凍係晴天無咩風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但香港都有乾凍，外國都有濕凍，只係頻率少，令人無咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />另外風係先過雨，同樣10度，大風係凍過無風有雨，晴天大風的話可能都係同無風有雨差唔多感覺，當然又大風又有雨一定最凍，凍過實際個溫度數字幾多就睇幾大風，但大雨細雨個體感唔會差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958331c23841825358c9bc10c95098962d24729d","tid":151401,"uid":79373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T11:45:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote