25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由我同櫻花負責開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家意見如何？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n赤巴同馬sir都有呢到ac既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係佢地開唔開先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c385a22ee0b7cd8c5fb49364ed5844b8ff99dc","tid":151401,"uid":42440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T15:50:56.000Z","msg":"濕度高水heat capacity高唔係應該多啲energy咩<br />\n咁濕凍應該熱啲先係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00273ac3286ad5407eed6b3104ad5fc2d2bdb6e","tid":151401,"uid":36650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:09:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-aI6DQDvm9Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-aI6DQDvm9Y&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=f204fd79\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-aI6DQDvm9Y</a><br />\n【低溫預警】本台於2017年3月15日0000時向荃灣、屯門、元朗、北區、西貢、沙田、觀塘、東區、離島及大埔發出低溫預警。"},{"pid":"3957e481b6e7f17a1bbc65a343a3ea0fbb43ee28","tid":151401,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:38:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>濕度高水heat capacity高唔係應該多啲energy咩<br />\n咁濕凍應該熱啲先係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n單純天氣情況一樣無雨無太陽風速一樣溫度一樣，濕度高係會暖d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc991128446eb1cfc1ebec3303e2bfa87eaad787","tid":151401,"uid":36650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:37:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bE73K-aQies\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbE73K-aQies&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=b0c2ca95\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bE73K-aQies</a><br />\n<br />\n【解除低溫預警】本台於2017年3月15日2300時解除所有低溫預警。          <br />\n【天氣概況】 預料東北季候風會喺未來兩三日為華南沿岸地區帶來清涼同多雲嘅天氣。<br />\n⚠注意事項<br />\n⭕在冬春季交替時，天氣乍暖還寒。留意天氣轉變，適時增減衣物。<br />\n⭕打算參加水上運動或進行海上工作人士請特別小心，以防大風大浪帶來的危險。<br />\n⭕受不穩定天氣影響，留意天氣變化，適時帶備雨具。<br />\n⭕回南天非常潮濕，注意室內防潮。能見度低，注意交通安全。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828abe76739252bbb83d92f16927cad5c7270509","tid":151401,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T01:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c92486e3481616d51836e644020523e43f18038e","tid":151401,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:06:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&quot;「資料一線通」不實用　難滿足用家需要<br />\n<br />\n另一業界人士Open Source Hong Kong（開源香港）主席馮振華亦指，「資料一線通」對用家而言相當匱乏，因網站數據種類有限且不實用。他舉例，網站發放的天氣資料格式並不普及，令他需要另向天文台付費購買服務才能取得相關資料。<br />\n<br />\n馮又批評，政府開放數據存在制度缺陷：「資料一線通」由資訊科技辦公室統籌，負責將各部門提供的數據資料整合。惟過去他與資科辦的會面，了解到資科辦「其實話唔到事」，質疑其所謂的部門與市民之間的「橋樑」角色似乎相當有限。他舉例，對上一次與當局會面已是數年前，而且市民不清楚資科辦如何與其他部門溝通，亦無與開發者等業界人士定期會面。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，官員不了解開放數據，擔心此舉會影響工作甚至因此「揹鑊」，要求政府盡快訂立檔案法，推動政府開放數據。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n(更正: 上一次我跟 OGCIO 會面是去年年尾，不過內容和回應都跟過往幾年來幾次會面都是一樣。)<br />\n<br />\n&quot;資科辦：一直有與業界溝通<br />\n<br />\n資科辦表示，一直透過不同途徑諮詢業界對開放數據的意見及訴求，包括參與研討會、及與專業團體、大學、數碼港及科技園等交流、了解最新發展。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n(我補充：但 OGCIO 已經兩三年很久沒有主動找 &quot;業界&quot; 諮詢開放數據的意見及訴求。有的都是莫乃光議員約 OGCIO 和 &quot;業界&quot; 坐下在立法會大樓會議室內談開放數據)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/77651/-%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A-%E6%A5%AD%E7%95%8C%E6%89%B9%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E6%85%8B%E5%BA%A6%E6%B6%88%E6%A5%B5-%E7%AA%92%E7%A4%99%E5%89%B5%E7%A7%91%E7%94%A2%E6%A5%AD-%E9%98%BB%E4%BA%BA%E7%99%BC%E9%81%94-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F77651%2F-%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A-%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%2595%258C%25E6%2589%25B9%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2585%258B%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%25A5%25B5-%25E7%25AA%2592%25E7%25A4%2599%25E5%2589%25B5%25E7%25A7%2591%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25A5%25AD-%25E9%2598%25BB%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2599%25BC%25E9%2581%2594-&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=1d2ee0a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/77651/-%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A-%E6%A5%AD%E7%95%8C%E6%89%B9%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E6%85%8B%E5%BA%A6%E6%B6%88%E6%A5%B5-%E7%AA%92%E7%A4%99%E5%89%B5%E7%A7%91%E7%94%A2%E6%A5%AD-%E9%98%BB%E4%BA%BA%E7%99%BC%E9%81%94-</a></blockquote><br />\n天文台啲資料係好有用<br />\n但又要申請版權，詳細紀錄或過去紀錄又要俾錢買<br />\n係而家講big data嘅今日係好唔方便"},{"pid":"fc15b56b13406527184c70b6b66e05a2a936840d","tid":151401,"uid":36650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:28:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KolVK8BTamc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKolVK8BTamc&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=b229ae42\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KolVK8BTamc</a><br />\n<br />\n【天氣概況】 預料東北季候風持續為廣東沿岸地區帶來清涼同多雲嘅天氣。預料一 道廣闊低壓槽會喺週末期間為華南地區帶嚟雷雨。       <br />\n<br />\n⚠注意事項<br />\n⭕在冬春季交替時，天氣乍暖還寒。留意天氣轉變，適時增減衣物。<br />\n⭕受不穩定天氣影響，留意天氣變化，適時帶備雨具。<br />\n====================<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"977bd0c18e27b1d6dd133e6092dea2f547a67cf2","tid":151401,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T00:19:06.000Z","msg":"週末低壓槽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59e211b48beefbf7d60bfddcb3b510bd20871a4","tid":151401,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:33:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>週末低壓槽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該幾頹下果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adfadf